Genetic testing in combination with preventive donepezil treatment for patients 
with amnestic mild cognitive impairment: an exploratory economic evaluation of 
personalized medicine.

Djalalov S(1), Yong J, Beca J, Black S, Saposnik G, Musa Z, Siminovitch K, 
Moretti M, Hoch JS.

